potential buyers to sell its Italian unit Crediop,  De Tijd 
reported without saying where it got the information.  Dexia holds 70 percent of Crediop and is required by the
European Commission to sell the unit by November 2012, according
to the report. The newspaper didnâ€™t identify the interested
